// Windows resource script — embeds the application icon into briarthorn.exe so
// Windows shows it in Explorer, the taskbar, and Alt-Tab. Windows uses the icon
// with the numerically lowest resource id as the executable's icon, so id 1.
//
// The path is relative to this .rc file's directory, which MSVC's rc.exe searches,
// so a bare filename resolves.
1 ICON "briarthorn.ico"
